l\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/幻灯片15.jpg\" alt=\"幻灯片15\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/幻灯片15.jpg 720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/幻灯片15-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone wp-image-539535 size-full\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/幻灯片16.jpg\" alt=\"幻灯片16\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/幻灯片16.jpg 720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/09/幻灯片16-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" /></p>\n","author":1051,"categories":[18270,18269,31660],"tags":[31705]}